1. *Operaciju* je pacijent dobro prebrodio. (The patient has recovered well from the operation.)

2. U narednoj nedelji ćemo izvršiti *operaciju*. (We will perform the operation next week.)

3. On je preživeo *operaciju*. (He survived the operation.)

4. Pre nego što započne *operaciju*, doktor mora da proveri lekove. (Before starting the operation, the doctor must check the medications.)

5. *Operaciju* će izvršiti najbolji tim u bolnici. (The best team in the hospital will perform the operation.)

6. Pre dva dana je uspešno završena *operaciju*. (The operation was successfully completed two days ago.)